CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1945, pg. 4, reads: Miss Ethel Lewis, charming daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Leonard Williams, of 717 Finland Street, was recently married to Pfc. Phillip H. Littlejohn, son of Mr. and Mrs. J. E. Littlejohn, of Horton Street.  The newlyweds are spending their honeymoon in New York. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ethel Lewis Littlejohn and Private first class Philip H. Littlejohn posed in Harris Studio
